<p>That'll give us a different cache key for each.  </p>
<p>Next, grab the key-value store itself with <code>$store = $this-&gt;keyValueFactory-&gt;get()</code>
and then the name of our store: <code>dino</code>. If the store <em>has</em> the key, return
<code>$store-&gt;get($key)</code> and save us from the long, slow 2 second sleep:</p>
